17 Notwithstanding any other provision of this chapter, no insurer in this state shall raise
18 rates on a private passenger motor vehicle insurance policy more often than once every
19 calendar year;"
20 SECTION 2.
21 This Act shall become effective on January 1, 2026, and shall apply to all policies issued,
22 delivered, issued for delivery, or renewed in this state on or after such date.
23 SECTION 3.
24 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
